```Go [sol1-Go]
func minOperations(nums []int, k int) int {
    sum := 0
    for _, num := range nums {
        sum += num
    }
    return sum % k
}
```

```Python [sol1-Python3]
class Solution:
    def minOperations(self, nums: List[int], k: int) -> int:
        return sum(nums) % k
```

```C [sol1-C]
int minOperations(int* nums, int numsSize, int k) {
    int sum = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i < numsSize; i++) {
        sum += nums[i];
    }
    return sum % k;
}
```

